That these little satellites
all over the world ocean

01:10:42.460 --> 01:10:43.800
gathering this data.

01:10:43.800 --> 01:10:46.090
Because we can handle the data.

01:10:46.090 --> 01:10:48.280
Modern computational
systems can handle it.

01:10:48.280 --> 01:10:51.620
It's just actually getting those
numbers and bringing them in.

01:10:51.620 --> 01:10:56.180
